<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="slow-adv">slow <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /sləʊ/    美 /sloʊ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>缓慢地；慢慢地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My watch goes slow.
我的表走得慢。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How slow the time passes!
时间过得真慢啊！</p></div></div>